@eugene_loh reposting BofA Securities memory team note:

"BofA forecasts Q3 DRAM contract prices to rise 5 to 17 percent QoQ. The low end assumes Samsung HBM3E qualification slips into late Q3; the high end assumes clean qualification by mid-July. Our central case is 11 percent. We note that TrendForce's published range is wider than our model implies at the low end."

— Reposted for visibility. Attribution: BofA Securities Memory Team.

